abag\n|[[Underbelly (venue)|Underbelly]], [[Cowgate]]<br/>[[Salisbury Playhouse]]<br/>[[SoHo Playhouse]]<br/>[[Wyndham's Theatre]]\n|<ref>{{cite web|title=Fleabag review|url=https://www.timeout.com/london/theatre/fleabag-review|website=Time Out|publisher=[[Time Out (magazine)#Time Out London|Time Out London]]|accessdate=4 August 2017}}</ref> <br/> <ref name=SalisburyPlayhouse-Fleabag-2015>{{cite web|title=A DryWrite and Soho Theatre Production: Fleabag|url=http://www.salisburyplayhouse.com/page/fleabag-2|website=[[Salisbury Playhouse]]|accessdate=25 September 2016|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150213213136/http://www.salisburyplayhouse.com/page/fleabag-2|archivedate=13 February 2015|date=February 2015}}</ref> <br/> <ref>{{cite web|title=Fleabag: A New Play|url=http://fleabagnyc.com/|website=Fleabag NYC|accessdate=28 April 2019|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190220003226/http://fleabagnyc.com/|archivedate=20 February 2019|date=February 2019}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Fleabag @ Wyndham's Theatre - Soho Theatre|url=https://sohotheatre.com/shows/fleabag-wyndhams-theatre/|website=Fleabag NYC|accessdate=3 May 2019|date=May 2019}}</ref>\n|-\n|2014\n|''The One''\n|Jo\n|Soho Theatre, London\n|<ref name=SohoTheatre-TheOne-2014>{{cite web|title=Soho Theatre present Fleabag|url=http://www.sohotheatre.com/whats-on/the-one/|website=[[Soho Theatre]]|accessdate=9 August 2016|date=February 2015}}</ref>\n|}\n\n===Writer===\n{|class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n|-\n! Year\n! Title\n! class=\"unsortable\" |Notes\n|-\n| 2014\n| ''[[Drifters (TV series)|Drifters]]''\n| 3 episodes\n|-\n|2018\u2013present\n|''[[Killing Eve]]''\n| Also executive producer; 4 episodes\n|-\n| 2020\n| ''[[No Time to Die]]''\n| Co-writer\n|-\n|}\n\n==Works and publications==\n* {{cite book|last1=Waller-Bridge|first1=Phoebe|title=Fleabag|date=1 January 2013|publisher=Nick Hern Books|location=London|isbn=978-1-84-842364-0|oclc=894546593}}\n\n==Awards==\n{| class=\"sortable wikitable\"\n|-\n! Year